com.htsmart.wristband.bean

类 SyncRawData

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.htsmart.wristband.bean.SyncRawData

  • public class SyncRawData
extends java.lang.Object
    Raw data from device synchronization.Represents a data value of 5 minutes at a time node. So the timeStamp is always an integer multiple of 5 minutes.

    For example, if type==TYPE_STEPS, timeStamp=18:00, value=50. This means that between 17:55-18:00, the number of steps is 50. And not 18:00 this moment, the number of steps 50.

    For example, if type==TYPE_SLEEP, timeStamp=18:00, value=SLEEP_STATUS_DEEP. This means that between 17:55-18:00, the sleep is always SLEEP_STATUS_DEEP.

      • timeStamp

        private int timeStamp
        Time stamp.Unit Seconds.

      • value

        private int value
        Value.

        when type==TYPE_STEPS, this is steps value.

        when type==TYPE_ULTRAVIOLET_RAYS, this is ultraviolet rays level.

        when type==TYPE_SLEEP, this is sleep status. There are three kinds of sleep status: SLEEP_STATUS_DEEP SLEEP_STATUS_SHALLOW SLEEP_STATUS_SOBER

        when type==TYPE_HEART_RATE, this is heart rate value.

        when type==TYPE_OXYGEN, this is oxygen value.

        when type==TYPE_BLOOD_PRESSURE, this is systolic pressure value.

        when type==TYPE_RESPIRATORY_RATE, this is respiratory rate value.

      • value2

        private int value2
        Value2.

        when type==TYPE_BLOOD_PRESSURE, this is diastolic pressure value.

        Other conditions have no effect.

        private int type
        Data type.

        TYPE_STEPS TYPE_ULTRAVIOLET_RAYS TYPE_SLEEP TYPE_HEART_RATE TYPE_OXYGEN TYPE_BLOOD_PRESSURE TYPE_RESPIRATORY_RATE
